And as for my family's personal energy crisis, I'm pleased to report that
my wife and I are once again hearing the ice maker rumble, watching the
best that cable TV has to offer and e-mailing our friends and family about
our unexpected (and not completely unpleasant) trip back in time to a
simpler style of life.


Paul Goodwin
For Cabot Wealth Advisory

